Admin --> UC28
UC28 .> UC28_1 : <<include>>
UC28 .> UC28_2 : <<include>>
UC28 .> UC28_3 : <<include>>
UC28 .> UC28_4 : <<include>>
UC28 .> UC28_5 : <<include>>

UC28_1 ..> DB : <<uses>>
UC28_2 ..> DB : <<uses>>

' VPS deployment
Admin --> UC29
UC29 .> UC29_1 : <<include>>
UC29 .> UC29_2 : <<include>>
UC29 .> UC29_3 : <<include>>
UC29 .> UC29_4 : <<include>>
UC29 .> UC29_5 : <<include>>

UC29_1 ..> VPS : <<uses>>

' Backup flow
Admin --> UC30
UC30 .> UC30_1 : <<include>>
UC30 .> UC30_2 : <<include>>
UC30 .> UC30_3 : <<include>>
UC30 .> UC30_4 : <<include>>

note right of UC29
  VPS deployment:
  - Automated setup
  - Docker support
  - Monitoring included
  - Auto-restart
